dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Sean Griffin. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Kathryn. Could you provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course, my policy number is five six two three eight and my date of birth is zero nine one zero one nine nine zero.
Thank you, Kathryn. One last thing, could you also confirm your current address and phone number on file with us?
My address is two four six Pine Street, Springfield, and my phone number is five five five eight nine zero two one.
Great, I have verified the information. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss or inquire about today, Kathryn?
I wanted to check the status of a claim I made last week.
I'll be happy to assist with that. Thank you for your time, Kathryn. I'm checking on the claim status now.
Thank you for your patience, Kathryn. Your claim is currently in the investigation process. We will keep you updated. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
Thank you for your time, Kathryn. Have a great day!
